snippet.title: Meghan Markle's Ellen Appearance Sparked 'Cringe' But Will It Be a Positive Move for Her Image? |GMB
snippet.description:
Meghan Markle appeared on Ellen this week where she talks about her life in America with her family and about Harry and Meghan's last night of freedom before their relationship became public. Journalist, Emily Andrews joins Ben and Charlotte to talk about the interview and what it could mean for their future. Watch the full interview on ITV2 next week.
Broadcast on 19/11/21
